294
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:14,839
without thinking about the consequences.

295
00:17:15,109 --> 00:17:16,400
And even if you break up,

296
00:17:16,400 --> 00:17:17,310
you both go your separate ways

297
00:17:17,310 --> 00:17:17,920
amicably, and you think

298
00:17:17,920 --> 00:17:19,319
you can still be friends.

299
00:17:19,349 --> 00:17:20,069
But her?

300
00:17:21,869 --> 00:17:23,130
You can afford to lose,

301
00:17:23,480 --> 00:17:24,280
but she can't.

302
00:17:28,750 --> 00:17:30,310
I just hope the world

303
00:17:31,160 --> 00:17:32,640
