306
00:17:44,770 --> 00:17:45,510
Come sit here!

307
00:17:45,510 --> 00:17:47,170
Let me put some medicine on it!

308
00:17:47,330 --> 00:17:48,030
It's really nothing.

309
00:17:48,030 --> 00:17:49,490
It'll be fine in a few days.

310
00:17:49,790 --> 00:17:51,440
