311
00:17:51,440 --> 00:17:52,530
Where's the bruise?

312
00:17:52,530 --> 00:17:53,860
It's just the lighting.

313
00:17:56,680 --> 00:17:57,200
Corn,

314
00:17:57,960 --> 00:17:59,290
don't be angry anymore.

315
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:00,660
