320
00:18:09,160 --> 00:18:10,560
when Jiang Bohan hit you?

321
00:18:12,680 --> 00:18:14,610
I was just pretending to upset him.

322
00:18:15,250 --> 00:18:15,660
Fine,

323
00:18:15,840 --> 00:18:17,380
you two are ganging up to annoy me, huh?

324
00:18:17,380 --> 00:18:18,680
Apply the ointment yourself.

325
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:19,510
I was wrong, okay?

326
00:18:19,510 --> 00:18:20,220
I was wrong. I was wrong.

327
00:18:20,220 --> 00:18:21,600
Don't be mad anymore. Please.

328
00:18:21,600 --> 00:18:22,340
I was wrong.

329
00:18:25,680 --> 00:18:26,440
Keep acting.

330
00:18:26,990 --> 00:18:28,450
It really hurts this time.

331
00:18:29,370 --> 00:18:30,270
Really?

332
00:18:32,090 --> 00:18:33,090
I'm just kidding.

333
00:18:34,140 --> 00:18:35,720
You Jingchu, don't be so childish!

334
00:18:35,720 --> 00:18:36,620
This really hurts!

335
00:18:36,620 --> 00:18:37,480
That's what you get for fighting.

336
00:18:37,480 --> 00:18:38,680
Will you fight again?

337
00:18:39,070 --> 00:18:39,920
No, I won't.

338
00:18:39,950 --> 00:18:41,280
No more fighting, okay?

339
00:18:41,510 --> 00:18:42,440
I'm leaving now.

